{"tid":1694272,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[警世]不要停，清算is coming","createTime":"2019-11-05T05:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T02:31:48.000Z","uid":57911,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"62d868b6d8fcf7fbe3f667b5cf344c6dd54b46ae","tid":1694272,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"見到好多爭論停戰云云<br />\n甚至Google十一月日程表都搵唔到<br />\n想講大家堅持到今日除咗係為咗理想為咗手足義士<br />\n仲有最重要嘅係為咗自己搏到盡拒絕清算<br />\n大家深信就算我哋停popo清算都唔會停<br />\n我哋休息popo都有得休息<br />\n記得起初UR爭拗唔好衝升旗禮唔好激嬲共產黨<br />\n到到今日大家日日Google曱維尼<br />\n其實大家都清楚無論激唔激嬲共產黨，DQ嘅決定權都喺共產黨嘅手<br />\n唔通佢推遲到十二月就停到十二月？<br />\n一個月咩人都拉鳩晒啦<br />\n義士們唔企出嚟唔代表popo唔會搵上門<br />\n<br />\n不要停，清算is coming<br />\n<br />\n和理非又好<br />\n超合作運動又好<br />\n不合作運動都好<br />\n總之唔好停，推爆佢，推到bam<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xENgXoO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxENgXoO.gif&h=3ce10586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df25fbab8427e487555cbfac29835dbc6521b69c","tid":1694272,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"推爆佢，推到bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb08fbda421ceaa80ba2e112ffe157f67afb830e","tid":1694272,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"[白票運動，正式開始]大黨無法止暴制亂，身為民建聯支持者，決定叫身邊藍絲投對家或白票<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1694260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1694260</a>"},{"pid":"32761ecf040eac134f9543b052045c4d34bee896","tid":1694272,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77ae4eef568e825f9f589c59553d5589046bf15b","tid":1694272,"uid":199926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQGgD4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQGgD4p.png&h=e2bb4e